+ * `r` argument is clamped up to scroll_top — that means \e[S/T (full-region
+ * scroll) and the LF-at-bottom path scroll the region only, while \e[L/M
+ * (insert/delete-at-cursor) scroll from the cursor down to scroll_bot. */
